# Copy to .env.local (git-ignored). In the DEFAULT proxy build you need NOTHING
# here — the LLM/realtime keys live in Supabase Edge Function secrets, not the APK
# (see supabase/functions/README.md).
#
# These are ONLY for local dev with the proxy turned off (VITE_PROXY=0), which
# bakes the keys into the bundle. Never ship a proxy-off build.
# VITE_PROXY=0
# VITE_OPENAI_KEY=sk-...
# VITE_DEEPINFRA_KEY=your-deepinfra-key
